OL,6,FThey are described as wearing dark
OL,7,Fclothing and a dark-coloured rucksack.
OL,9,FGuernsey Police says: "This was a
OL,10,Fparticularly violent offence and
OL,11,FCrimestoppers is offering a reward of
OL,12,F#750 for information leading to the
OL,13,Farrest, charge and conviction of the
OL,14,Foffender."
OL,16,FAnyone with dash cam video, CCTV
OL,17,Ffootage or other details is asked to
OL,18,Fcall officers on 01481 222222 or
OL,19,Fanonymously on 0800 555111.
